</article><!-- #post-## -->

			
				
<article id="post-208" class="post-208 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-indoor">
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.heliovolt.net/newest-office-furnitures-better-living/" rel="bookmark">Newest Office Furnitures for a Better Living</a></h1>
				<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="posted-on">Posted on <a href="http://www.heliovolt.net/newest-office-furnitures-better-living/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2016-07-09T09:29:11+00:00">July 9, 2016</time><time class="updated" datetime="2016-07-12T18:00:20+00:00">July 12, 2016</time></a></span><span class="byline"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.heliovolt.net/author/heliovol/">Ansley Jac</a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
				<p>More than one third of your working day is spent while sitting in the office. Such professionals require proper seating alongside a few stretches that offer little impact when trying to relieve the strain and stress on your back. The healthiest option is through getting a chair that fits well, which not only prevents sitting posture problems, but also improves the quality of job performance. Please do not compare a chair with a <a href="http://www.heliovolt.net/smart-telescopes-can-make-astronomy-enjoyable/">telescope</a> or an expensive watch that you buy for yourself, keep in mind that every penny is for your health in this investment.</p>
<p>With so many types of office chairs in the market today, it might be very overwhelming for most of us when it comes to choosing that best office chair model. Many of them are labeled “ergonomic”, but that doesn’t guarantee you full satisfaction. Instead of spending hours or days browsing volumes of seats in different websites, we have simplified everything for you. Therefore, our unbiased list of top five tested ones will help you make the right decision.If you are looking especially comfortable chair reviews you can visit <a href="http://www.mycomfyoffice.com/most-comfortable-office-chair/" target="_blank">mycomfyoffice</a> website.</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Herman Miller Aeron Office Chair</strong></li>
</ol>
<p>Herman Miller chairs have been taking up bigger market all over the world due to high quality. But not all appear in top lists of the best seats, but this Aeron chair has made it. It not only offers sturdy support and comfort, but also a stylish asset to put in your office. It is impossible to have a chair that has all ergonomic features, but Aeron is one of kind comfortable office furniture that any professional may want to use. However, it lacks the headrest and may not be suitable for those looking for a chair with that specific feature.</p>
<ol start="2">
<li>Stealcase<strong> Amia Office Chair</strong></li>
</ol>
<p>Ease of adjustments, comfort, and solid support makes this chair stand out. Based on customer comments and opinions, this chair is quite valuable and worthy to have in an office. Apart from its elegant looking, it has well-positioned armrests and nice-fitted back. Even though some people may be scared away by the relatively high price, actually you pay for what you get. <a href="http://www.nhs.uk/Livewell/workplacehealth/Pages/howtositcorrectly.aspx" target="_blank">Health in the office is more important</a>, and therefore you can consider investing in this ergonomic office chair.<img class=" wp-image-209 alignright" src="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/offices-on-sale.jpg" alt="office chairs" width="280" height="187" srcset="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/offices-on-sale.jpg 763w, http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/offices-on-sale-300x200.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 280px) 100vw, 280px" /></p>
<ol start="3">
<li><strong>Herman Miller Embody Chair</strong></li>
</ol>
<p>If you have visited several offices for both middle and large scale companies, many managers use this Embody chair. It is ergonomically designed to offer healthy working experience, as well as eliminating frequent backaches and stress. In terms of comfort and function, this chair has been rated high by most users. In addition, it has an adorable design that adds value of your office. If looking for a chair to work with a slight recline, this can be a better option. Also, it feels good even when sitting in an upright pose.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<ol start="4">
<li><strong>Steelcase Think Chair</strong></li>
</ol>
<p>This chair is suitable for different body types, but it is not fit for anyone taller than 6 feet due to its seat pan. It has several features of an ergonomic chair, ensuring comfortable seating ideal for office work. You can adjust to fit variety of heights, and many users say it works incredibly well. Based on what happy users said, the back is made up of breathable material that keeps their backs cool throughout the day. Even though it is not best rated like its counterpart Amia chair, it can be a good selection for working professionals.</p>
<ol start="5">
<li><strong>Herman Miller Sayl Chair</strong></li>
</ol>
<p>This is another amazing designed ergonomic chair, though it lacks a sturdy back support. However, people have different choices when it comes to comfort, and probably it is the best option for many. Due to its design nature, a few users say it is ideal for meetings or conferences. Others say it cannot be used for long hours, especially for big people. Therefore, it can be perfect if you are not looking for a full-time office chair.<img class=" wp-image-210 alignleft" src="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/comfortable-office-chairs-.jpg" alt="comfortable office chairs" width="336" height="162" srcset="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/comfortable-office-chairs-.jpg 870w, http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/comfortable-office-chairs--300x145.jpg 300w, http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/comfortable-office-chairs--768x371.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 336px) 100vw, 336px" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Things have remarkably changed over the years, since you can buy a chair based on your comfort needs. You can order customized chairs, which means you will be the only user. Buying an office chair is a long term investment that doesn’t require faster decision. So, you can inform the sellers what you want, and compare all different types they offer. This will help you get the best of what you wanted, without unwelcoming surprise down the line.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Stiff back is one of the most common complaints among office workers. Neck and wrist pain are also other problems, which occur due to sedentary stretching and wrong chair height. Ergonomic chairs are designed to address these troubles by improving comfort, as well as functionality. Therefore, it is advisable to consider both comfort and functionality when choosing an office chair. Read our post: <a href="http://www.heliovolt.net/latest-massage-chair-technologies/">Buying a Massage Chair</a>.</p>

			</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="cat-links">Categories: <a href="http://www.heliovolt.net/category/indoor/" rel="category tag">Indoor</a> </span>	</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
</article><!-- #post-## -->

			
				
<article id="post-22" class="post-22 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-solar-power">
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.heliovolt.net/latest-innovations-solar-power-smart-homes/" rel="bookmark">Latest Innovations In Solar Power for Smart Homes</a></h1>
				<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="posted-on">Posted on <a href="http://www.heliovolt.net/latest-innovations-solar-power-smart-homes/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2015-12-23T05:29:21+00:00">December 23, 2015</time><time class="updated" datetime="2016-06-15T01:15:49+00:00">June 15, 2016</time></a></span><span class="byline"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.heliovolt.net/author/heliovol/">Ansley Jac</a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
				<h2>Overview</h2>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-64" src="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Latest-Innovations-In-Solar-Power-1.jpg" alt="Latest Innovations In Solar Power 1" width="640" height="360" srcset="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Latest-Innovations-In-Solar-Power-1.jpg 640w, http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Latest-Innovations-In-Solar-Power-1-300x169.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" />Many people globally have tried to move a step higher in ensuring that their smart house simplifies their lives with ease. As luck would have it, several technocrats have also been spending quality time thinking on how best they can increase the utility of these <a href="http://www.heliovolt.net/the-ecological-dream-house/" target="_blank">smart homes</a>. One of these ways include coming up with solar power innovations that can achieve their desired effect.</p>
<h2>Electric car solar charging</h2>
<p>Solar panels have become one of the most essential devices to have in some smart homes. They have the ability to tap and harness the solar energy and convert it into a form that can readily be utilized by its user. Charging of electric cars has seen a joyous daybreak as they can now be charged by the energy harnessed by the solar rooftops – thanks to the developers. This increases convenience since the home owners no longer need to worry about the charging of their cars. The solar energy trapped by the solar panel is then utilized by the car in its charging through a cable connected mostly in the anterior part of these cars (but it depends on the nature and type of the car as others |ingest’ the energy via other parts of the car)</p>
<h2>The home energy management system</h2>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-68" src="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Latest-Innovations-In-Solar-Power-3-1024x731.jpg" alt="Latest Innovations In Solar Power 3" width="780" height="557" srcset="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Latest-Innovations-In-Solar-Power-3-1024x731.jpg 1024w, http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Latest-Innovations-In-Solar-Power-3-300x214.jpg 300w, http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Latest-Innovations-In-Solar-Power-3-768x548.jpg 768w, http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Latest-Innovations-In-Solar-Power-3.jpg 1180w" sizes="(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px" />The home energy management system abbreviated as HEMS is another innovation in smart homes. These systems run on small computers which have the potential of collecting all the solar energy consumption data from any electric meter of that home and its vicinage. These electric meters include the <a href="http://www.fsec.ucf.edu/en/consumer/solar_electricity/basics/how_pv_system_works.htm" target="_blank">photovoltaic system</a>, the heat pump, electric vehicle or any other general household device that records the amount of current that passes through it within a given period of time.</p>
<p>At any time of the day, the homeowner can track the individual and general power consumption. This is because the system has a display where the home owner can see and read the power consumption. In addition to that, it is from this system that the homeowner is in a position to access if the solar power available is able to charge his/her electric car.</p>
<h2>New advanced solar panels</h2>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-70" src="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Latest-Innovations-In-Solar-Power-2-2.jpg" alt="Latest Innovations In Solar Power 3" width="500" height="392" srcset="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Latest-Innovations-In-Solar-Power-2-2.jpg 500w, http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Latest-Innovations-In-Solar-Power-2-2-300x235.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" />In most cases, the solar panels are the widely used intermediate device to harness and output the solar energy. Smart homes have another reason to embark on solar panels. This is due to several features introduced that guarantee high efficiency as far as harnessing and outputting is concerned. One such feature includes their design. They are currently manufactured with a uniquely concave design that automatically rotates to follow the <a href="http://www.wikihow.com/Determine-Direction-Using-the-Sun" target="_blank">direction of the sun</a>. This is to not only ensure that they absorb as much <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Solar_energy" target="_blank">solar energy</a> as possible and also of relatively high intensity.</p>
<p>Technocrats have also found a way of increasing the solar panel efficiency and simultaneously lowering their cost. This is due to the employment of the very best silicon in the panel system. For maximum output possible, of late, high-capacity inverters have also been utilized. These produce a certain twist of innovation in the solar power industry.</p>
<h3>Conclusion</h3>
<p>The innovations in the solar power have greatly transitioned the way we live and manage our smart homes. All these latest innovations have made life simpler due to the efficiency achieved and also guarantees a relatively Carbon (IV) Oxide (CO2) free home since solar energy is known to be highly environment friendly. It’s time to adopt these innovations in smart homes.</p>

			</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="cat-links">Categories: <a href="http://www.heliovolt.net/category/solar-power/" rel="category tag">Solar Power</a> </span>	</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
