<article id="post-25" class="post-25 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-indoor">
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.heliovolt.net/will-smart-tankless-water-heater-help-safe-energy/" rel="bookmark">How Will Smart Tankless Water Heater Help Safe Energy?</a></h1>
				<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="posted-on">Posted on <a href="http://www.heliovolt.net/will-smart-tankless-water-heater-help-safe-energy/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2015-08-06T05:28:40+00:00">August 6, 2015</time><time class="updated" datetime="2016-06-15T01:17:59+00:00">June 15, 2016</time></a></span><span class="byline"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.heliovolt.net/author/heliovol/">Ansley Jac</a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
				<h2>Introduction</h2>
<p><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-107" src="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/How-Will-Smart-Tankless-Water-Heater-Help-Safe-Energy-1-266x300.jpg" alt="How Will Smart Tankless Water Heater Help Safe Energy" width="266" height="300" srcset="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/How-Will-Smart-Tankless-Water-Heater-Help-Safe-Energy-1-266x300.jpg 266w, http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/How-Will-Smart-Tankless-Water-Heater-Help-Safe-Energy-1.jpg 395w" sizes="(max-width: 266px) 100vw, 266px" />Tankless water heaters have not been around for very long. However, in the short period that they have been around, they <a href="http://www.heliovolt.net/newest-water-treatment-devices-home-usage/" target="_blank">have made a noticeable impact on people</a>. Their popularity continues to grow in part due to advertising and in part due to the quality, they offer. For a long time, developments in water heating systems seemed to have plateaued. That was until these tankless systems were invented.</p>
<h2>How Do They Work?</h2>
<p>As the name implies, these <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Water_heating" target="_blank">heating systems</a> do not have a storage unit. Essentially, water is only heated when it is required. The heating system can either be centrally located or at the pint of exit. In the centralized systems, the water is heated much like the traditional way but the heater activates when the flow is detected.</p>
<p>The centralized system has some inefficiency. For one, it cannot reliably heat the entire house if all the outlets were being used at once. This can be a <a href="http://www.menshealth.com/grooming/ask-mh-shower-morning-vs-night" target="_blank">problem in the morning</a> when people are taking showers and others are doing dishes in the kitchen. To overcome this problem, the point of use systems were created. They can either be gas powered or electric powered. The choice of system usually depends on the costs of energy in the area where one lives. There is also less heat lost as energy travels through the pipes in this decentralized systems.</p>
<h2>How Do They Save Energy?</h2>
<p>The main way they do this is by ensuring water is only heated when it is required. With storage containers, the water may be liable to lose heat over time in the storage tank. In the storage tank systems, one always has to have a pilot light burning. This little flame consumes energy all year round. Cumulatively, it is a lot of energy that goes to waste.</p>
<p><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-108" src="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/How-Will-Smart-Tankless-Water-Heater-Help-Safe-Energy-2-300x213.jpg" alt="How Will Smart Tankless Water Heater Help Safe Energy" width="300" height="213" srcset="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/How-Will-Smart-Tankless-Water-Heater-Help-Safe-Energy-2-300x213.jpg 300w, http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/How-Will-Smart-Tankless-Water-Heater-Help-Safe-Energy-2-768x546.jpg 768w, http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/How-Will-Smart-Tankless-Water-Heater-Help-Safe-Energy-2.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" />Tankless water systems do not have this problem. The system only works when heat is required. The result is that over time huge savings in energy use can be seen. There is also the fact that traditional systems require quite a bit of time to heat up all the water efficiently. People who have been unfortunate enough to shower last know this problem. This problem is eliminated with tankless systems.</p>
<p>Another way in which tankless systems are more efficient is in the durability of the system. Most traditional systems scarcely make it through to ten years. If they manage to go beyond that, they are inefficient and require a lot of money to maintain. Tankless systems can have a lifetime of about twenty years. Furthermore, they require very few repairs. This is because they use few and durable components. This can lead to huge cost savings in the long term.</p>
<h3>Conclusion</h3>
<p>It is quite clear that tankless water systems are quite efficient. In addition, they can fit into any size of a house and do not need special storage space and pipe coverings. People who want to buy these systems should consider a few issues such as the cost of energy and regulations in their locality. This will help them determine if they make any savings.</p>

			</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="cat-links">Categories: <a href="http://www.heliovolt.net/category/indoor/" rel="category tag">Indoor</a> </span>	</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
</article><!-- #post-## -->

			
				
<article id="post-17" class="post-17 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-indoor">
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.heliovolt.net/latest-showerhead-innovations/" rel="bookmark">What Are the Latest Showerhead Innovations?</a></h1>
				<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="posted-on">Posted on <a href="http://www.heliovolt.net/latest-showerhead-innovations/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2015-07-17T05:32:28+00:00">July 17, 2015</time><time class="updated" datetime="2016-06-15T01:18:18+00:00">June 15, 2016</time></a></span><span class="byline"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.heliovolt.net/author/heliovol/">Ansley Jac</a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
				<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-105" src="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/What-Are-the-Latest-Showerhead-Innovations-2.jpg" alt="What Are the Latest Showerhead Innovations" width="680" height="471" srcset="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/What-Are-the-Latest-Showerhead-Innovations-2.jpg 680w, http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/What-Are-the-Latest-Showerhead-Innovations-2-300x208.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" />Since their invention in the 20th Century, shower heads have continued to evolve and become more functional. From a simple device that simply allowed people to free their hands for bathing only, the shower head has gone a revolution in the few centuries it has been in use. Modern shower heads offer the ability to offload stress and even cut down on the water bill.</p>
<h2>Magnetic Shower Heads</h2>
<p>This shower head envisions all the challenges that a person faces when they are using a shower head. For one, <a href="http://www.heliovolt.net/newest-water-treatment-devices-home-usage/" target="_blank">the presence of soap</a> in the eyes makes it hard to see where to place a detachable shower head. This technology employs magnetism to help individuals put the shower head back in place with little effort. They intentionally include an audible click to ensure one knows it is firmly in place.</p>
<h2>Shower Flow</h2>
<p>This is one of the best innovations in shower technology. The shower head comes fitted with technology that enables it to control the flow of water and there are various types to choose from, ranking from low to high with options such as rain shower also to choose from. However, this does no dull the showering experiencing. To get over this, the shower head is fitted with a way to mix air with water. Thus, one gets the same full effect of a shower while using less water. This is great for areas where water costs a fortune.</p>
<h2>Bluetooth Speakers</h2>
<p>This is another innovative idea for shower heads that is fast catching on. Instead of having the speakers close by in the bathroom, the shower head is fitted with speakers internally. This can be hooked up to any Bluetooth device for an awesome showering experience. One can play their favorite tunes as they take a shower, thus helping the mind to relax. The speakers are made waterproof this there is no risk of someone being zapped as they shower.</p>
<h2>Rain Shower Heads</h2>
<p><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-104" src="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/What-Are-the-Latest-Showerhead-Innovations-1-300x245.jpg" alt="What Are the Latest Showerhead Innovations" width="300" height="245" srcset="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/What-Are-the-Latest-Showerhead-Innovations-1-300x245.jpg 300w, http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/What-Are-the-Latest-Showerhead-Innovations-1.jpg 660w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" />This innovative invention has revolutionized how people take showers. It takes the form of a wide shower head, which sends down water in narrow streams just like rain. The rain or waterfall can be further enhanced using flow control. Essentially, the shower head mixes water with air and then increases flow. This leads to an awesome experience where one feels like they are standing in the rain from the comfort of their home.</p>
<h2>Variable Jets</h2>
<p>This is another major innovation in shower heads. Some shower heads come with over six different types of flows and jets. All these jets are essential for a<a href="http://www.gq.com/gallery/best-nighttime-shower-products" target="_blank"> relaxing shower</a> experience. The different types of jets can easily be switched using a simple dial. This makes the showering experience quite awesome.</p>
<h2>Finish</h2>
<p>This area has undergone massive innovation. Originally, shower heads were made of a similar style with a simple finish. However, now one can choose the finish they like on their shower heads. This is all part of interior design, where shower heads play an increasingly huge role. There is no reason for one to be stuck with a dull finish that does not relate to the interior of the bathroom. You can check more shower heads on <a href="http://www.finestshower.com" target="_blank">finestshower.com</a></p>
<h3>Conclusion</h3>
<p>Since their invention over a hundred years ago, the shower head has become an important fixture in the house. It can be a source of relaxation and visual appeal. Choose wisely to get the best of both.</p>

			</div><!-- .entry-content -->

