</article><!-- #post-## -->

			
				
<article id="post-10" class="post-10 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-indoor">
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.heliovolt.net/kitchen-faucet-innovations/" rel="bookmark">Kitchen Faucet Innovations</a></h1>
				<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="posted-on">Posted on <a href="http://www.heliovolt.net/kitchen-faucet-innovations/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2015-03-18T05:18:21+00:00">March 18, 2015</time><time class="updated" datetime="2016-06-15T01:19:29+00:00">June 15, 2016</time></a></span><span class="byline"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.heliovolt.net/author/heliovol/">Ansley Jac</a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
				<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-93" src="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Kitchen-Faucet-Innovations-1.jpg" alt="Kitchen Faucet Innovations 1" width="667" height="500" srcset="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Kitchen-Faucet-Innovations-1.jpg 667w, http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Kitchen-Faucet-Innovations-1-300x225.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 667px) 100vw, 667px" />A kitchen is one of the most important and most used places in a home. Water is a basic thing in the kitchen and is therefore indispensable. The water runs through the faucets on the sinks, showers and other water supplied areas in the house. In regard to that, kitchen faucets should not be underestimated when it comes to providing clean water through the kitchen. The position, make and size of the faucet play a major role in the accessibility of <a href="http://www.heliovolt.net/newest-water-treatment-devices-home-usage/" target="_blank">water in the entire house</a>. The size and type of the faucet also makes work easier hence saves time. One should also consider the style and function of the faucet.</p>
<h2>Faucet Spray</h2>
<p>This is a kind of faucet which is made in a special angle to supply water with a force. It helps in sweeping away food and remains on the dishes. It has been made in a way that one needs to press a button and the water comes out in a spray form. This makes work easier by saving time while rinsing the utensils. In addition to that, it helps in cleansing the sink after washing utensils. The force of water removes dirt and food remains from the corners of the sink. Learn more over at <a href="http://www.kitchenfaucetcenter.com/">www.kitchenfaucetcenter.com</a> to get to learn about the best kitchen faucets.</p>
<h2>Tall Drink</h2>
<p><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-94" src="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Kitchen-Faucet-Innovations-2-300x195.jpg" alt="Kitchen Faucet Innovations 1" width="300" height="195" srcset="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Kitchen-Faucet-Innovations-2-300x195.jpg 300w, http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Kitchen-Faucet-Innovations-2.jpg 485w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" />Most of the modern kitchens contain faucets with higher spouts. This mostly helps in providing room for big and longer water containers. According to an article published by Sharon O`Malley in March, 2013, modern kitchen faucets innovations makes chores easier to manage. She also highlights that the prices of the modern faucets and sinks have increased compared to the older faucets which were made of ceramics.</p>
<h2>Controlled Flow</h2>
<p>Kitchen faucets should be controllable when it comes to the flow of water. There are entrepreneurs who have filled in the gap to provide this products and services. For instance, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moen_%28company%29" target="_blank">Moen</a> is a company situated in North America which uses modern technology to make faucets. They have various selections and designs of controlled faucets. Some of these include;</p>
<p><strong><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-95" src="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Kitchen-Faucet-Innovations-3-300x225.jpg" alt="Kitchen Faucet Innovations 1" width="300" height="225" srcset="http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Kitchen-Faucet-Innovations-3-300x225.jpg 300w, http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Kitchen-Faucet-Innovations-3-768x576.jpg 768w, http://www.heliovolt.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Kitchen-Faucet-Innovations-3.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" />1. Faucets which respond to motion &#8211;</strong>The flow of water is controlled with a sensor when placing the hands on top of the faucet. Immediately you remove the hand, the water stops from flowing. These kinds are commonly used in five star hotels and modern homes. Thomas Tylicki, a Moen senior product specialist puts it that there is no other digital kitchen faucet that makes performing tasks in the kitchen easier and delivers this kind of experience.</p>
<p><strong>2. Magnetix – </strong>This type of faucet uses magnetic force to control the flow of water. Consequently, it leads to a significant reduction of water loss.</p>
<p><strong>3. io Digital –</strong> The flow and temperature of water is controlled using a remote control. The remote control contains buttons indicating the temperature in the water and the pressure the water is using.</p>
<p><strong>4. Power Clean –</strong> It is a kind of faucet technology that contains flash and improved power. The faucet has a handle on the side to control the flow by minimizing and maximizing the amount of water needed. You can read more about the best kitchen faucets on <a href="http://www.faucetmag.com" target="_blank">faucetmag.com</a></p>
<h3>Conclusion</h3>
<p>It is most people`s dream to make work easier in their day to day life. Work can be made easier in the kitchen using the modern technology of innovating and repairing faucets. Companies that offer efficient and affordable faucets have been opened and people should take this opportunity to improve their homes. Due to high demand of water and increase in population, modern faucets should be used to control water flow hence reducing water wastage through high consumption. The modern technology in the faucets also helps in maintaining good hygiene. This is due to easy cleaning of surfaces that water flow could not reach using old day’s faucets.</p>

			</div><!-- .entry-content -->

